face.note: Face detection coordinates for this face, along with live confidence levels.

heart_rate.note: Estimate of the global heart rate using pos method. This method is not capable of providing a confidence estimate, hence returning 1.

ppg_waveform.note: Estimate of the ppg waveform using pos method. This method is not capable of providing a confidence estimate, hence returning 1.

running_heart_rate.note: Estimate of the running heart rate using VitalLens, along with frame-wise confidences between 0 and 1.

message: The provided values are estimates and should be interpreted according to the provided confidence levels ranging from 0 to 1. The VitalLens API is not a medical device and its estimates are not intended for any medical purposes.
